message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $110. I believe it's worth a lot to you, and this is a fair price.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your willingness to sell the product. I am willing to pay $95 for it.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your position, but I'm looking for something closer to $105. This product offers a lot of value, and I'm confident you'll find it worth the investment.
I appreciate your offer, Alice. Considering the value of the product, I would like to propose a price of $100.
